---
title: "constructor (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init_parent: PriceManager(adminRoleTransferDelay, admin, verifierProxy, linkToken, feedInfos)
    q_init_parent --> q_check_zero: check assetOut and assetOutReceiver
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: assetOut == address(0) OR assetOutReceiver == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_check_zero --> q_set_values: both non-zero
    q_set_values --> q_check_min_pm: setMinBidUsdValue, setAssetOut, setAssetOutReceiver, setFeeAggregator
    q_check_min_pm --> q_revert_pm: minPriceMultiplier == 0
    q_revert_pm --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue()
    q_check_min_pm --> q_set_pm: minPriceMultiplier > 0
    q_set_pm --> [*]: i_minPriceMultiplier = minPriceMultiplier, emit MinPriceMultiplierSet

    note right of q_set_values
        INV-001: assetOut and assetOutReceiver must be non-zero addresses
        INV-002: minPriceMultiplier is immutable after construction
        INV-003: minBidUsdValue must be non-zero
    end note
